OL,3,CPlaid Cymru on course to be largest
OL,4,Cparty in the Senedd according to
OL,5,Clatest poll
OL,7,FPlaid Cymru has jumped ahead to be the
OL,8,Fpredicted largest party in the Senedd
OL,9,FElection according to the latest ITV
OL,10,FCymru Wales opinion poll.
OL,12,FThe findings, released two days before
OL,13,Fpolls open, show Rhun ap Iorwerth's
OL,14,Fparty with 33% of the vote share, four
OL,15,Fpercentage points ahead of Reform UK
OL,16,Fat 29%.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
