CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778097963
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru on course to be largest
OL,4,Cparty in the Senedd according to
OL,5,Clatest poll
OL,7,FWhen looking at Westminster voting
OL,8,Fintentions, Plaid Cymru continues to
OL,9,Flead with an increase in support for
OL,10,Fthem and Reform, while support has
OL,11,Flowered for the Greens and Labour.
OL,13,FDr Jac Larner from Cardiff
OL,14,FUniversity's Welsh Governance Centre
OL,15,Fsays the broad shape of Thursday's
OL,16,Fresult is now "fairly clear", even if
OL,17,Fprecise seat totals remain uncertain.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
