FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778097963
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru on course to be largest
OL,4,Cparty in the Senedd according to
OL,5,Clatest poll
OL,7,FHe added: "Plaid Cymru go into
OL,8,Felection day on 33 percent with Reform
OL,9,Fon 29. Whereas the previous YouGov
OL,10,Fpoll had the two parties tied at 29
OL,11,Fpercent each.
OL,13,F"Plaid appear to have opened a small
OL,14,Fgap in the final days but this still
OL,15,Fremains an incredibly close race. It
OL,16,Falso highlights how relatively small
OL,17,Fchanges in vote share can have
OL,18,Foutsized impacts in terms of seat
OL,19,Fallocation.
OL,26,@oD@KOUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778097963
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru on course to be largest
OL,4,Cparty in the Senedd according to
OL,5,Clatest poll
OL,7,F"That four-point lead is translating
OL,8,Finto a projected 43 seats against
OL,9,FReform's 34. Add Labour's projected 12
OL,10,Fseats, the Greens' 2 and the Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrats' 1, and the arithmetic for a
OL,12,Fprogressive majority government `
OL,13,Frequiring 49 of 96 seats ` looks
OL,14,Fconsiderably more comfortable than
OL,15,Fmany anticipated. Again however, even
OL,16,Ftiny changes that are too small for
OL,17,Fpolls to detect could mean the
OL,18,Feventual result is very different.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,495,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1778097963
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru on course to be largest
OL,4,Cparty in the Senedd according to
OL,5,Clatest poll
OL,7,F"That picture is broadly consistent
OL,8,Fwith where the polling consensus has
OL,9,Fsettled across multiple firms in
OL,10,Frecent weeks, with Plaid in the low-to-
OL,11,Fmid thirties, Reform in the high
OL,12,Ftwenties, and Labour anchored in low
OL,13,Fdouble figures.
OL,15,F"The more significant story for
OL,16,FThursday is therefore not the headline
OL,17,Fvote shares but what happens in the
OL,18,Froom afterwards and on that question,
OL,19,Fthe 43 percent of voters who expect
OL,20,FPlaid to lead the next government may
OL,21,Fwell be right."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
